
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Climate Dashboard</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial; margin: 40px; }
        h1 { color: #2c3e50; }
        .plot { margin: 20px 0; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>🌍 African Climate Analysis Dashboard</h1>
    <h3>Supporting Ethiopia's COP32 Preparation</h3>
    
    <div class="plot">
        <h2>Temperature Trends (2015-2026)</h2>
        <img src="temperature_trends.png" width="800">
    </div>
    
    <h2>Key Findings</h2>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Sudan</strong> is most vulnerable: 2,694 extreme heat days</li>
        <li><strong>Ethiopia</strong> is least vulnerable: 0 extreme heat days</li>
        <li>Sudan average temperature: 28.8°C</li>
        <li>Ethiopia average temperature: 16.1°C</li>
    </ul>
    
    <h2>Vulnerability Ranking</h2>
    <table border="1" cellpadding="8">
        <tr><th>Country</th><th>Avg Temp (°C)</th><th>Extreme Heat Days</th></tr>
        <tr><td>Sudan</td><td>28.8</td><td>2,694</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Nigeria</td><td>26.7</td><td>0</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Tanzania</td><td>26.8</td><td>0</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Kenya</td><td>20.4</td><td>0</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Ethiopia</td><td>16.1</td><td>0</td></tr>
    </table>
    
    <p><i>Data source: NASA POWER (2015-2026)</i></p>
</body>
</html>
